<% end %>

<div class="md:mt-4 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
  <h1 class="source-serif font-semibold text-center text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
    Pagecord: A Better Substack Alternative
  </h1>

  <div class="md:text-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-y-4">
    <p class="mt-8 md:mt-12">
      Substack charges you $50 to use your own domain. They take 10% of your revenue. They're VC-backed and haven't turned a profit despite being around since 2017.
    </p>
    <p>
      Pagecord is different. No revenue share. Built by one person, profitable from day one, and will be around for the long haul. Plus you can blog by email—just hit send and you're published.
    </p>
    <p>
      Open source. Classic plan is free forever. Premium is $<%= localised_price %>/year and includes custom domains, analytics, and more.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-8 mb-4 md:text-xl">
    <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
      <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-medium p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm btn-primary text-xl">Get your FREE account today</div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

